## Strategies:
```javascript
// Cache-first
async function fetchData() {
    const cached = await localDB.get('data');
    if (cached) return cached;

    try {
        const fresh = await api.get('/data');
        await localDB.set('data', fresh);
        return fresh;
    } catch (e) {
        return cached; // Fallback
    }
}
```

## Options:
- SQLite
- Realm
- AsyncStorage
- IndexedDB (PWA)
